data.description: WELCOME tto your 5 bedroom country estate! when you pull into the long drive way you will love the corner lot and no neighbor directly across the street. The curb appeal is very inviting and comfortable. From your first step in you will feel at "HOME". The formal living room or office has vaulted ceilings and beautiful barn doors with a great view. The large kitchen offers tons of cabinets and counter space with an open feel to the dinging room and living room. On the second floor you will be in love with the laundry room and storage on the main bedroom level. The owners suite is seperate from  bedrooms two and three providing a sense of privacy. The lower level offers accress to the garage and the back yard with a large living room with a fireplace and half bath. The sub-basement has been finished to provide 2 more conforming rooms and a full bathroom. The space offered in your new home is outstanding. The outdoor spaces are great for entertaining and enjoying every chance you get.
